OL,3,GNorthern Ireland
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FA mostly cloudy day with some
OL,6,Fpatchy rain. Becoming mainly dry
OL,7,Fduring the afternoon with some bright
OL,8,Fspells coming through later towards
OL,9,Fthe North Coast.
OL,10,
OL,11,CTonight:FIt will be mostly cloudy
OL,12,Fduring the evening and overnight with
OL,13,Fa few light showers around. Some clear
OL,14,Fspells developing later.
OL,15,
OL,16,CMonday:FA dry day with good sunny
OL,17,Fspells and light winds. A few showers
OL,18,Farriving from the northwest in the
OL,19,Fevening.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
